[src:bioenergy/2022-in-climate-change] This article documents events, research findings, scientific and technological advances, and human actions to measure, predict, mitigate, and adapt to the effects of global warming and climate change—during the year 2022.
[src:bioenergy/2022-in-climate-change] A 2022 study found that the public substantially underestimates the degree of scientific consensus that humans are causing climate change.
